channel.title: PI - Need help making Public - *RSGP REWARD*
channel.description:
Hey guys, I have coded my server alot lately and have the urge to show my friends the beta.
But the thing is I'm not very bright with the client.java files and changing the IP's and crap...
NOW DON'T think im one of those people that don't have everything set up.
I have my Source/Client...blahblahblah... No-IP Set and Running Portwarded/w AT&T And some knowledge about setting servers to being public, NOT the whole base of it though.
EVERYTHINGS right, I used a site to tell me if the port is online and it's online.
So now, all that's left is actually making it public.
REWARD: 1-3Mil RSGP (Cash depends on how much stuff you change/fix) ***IF*** people can login.
I am only exepting help by Teamviewer or Msn since I suck with text learning.
Thanks! If you're interested, please comment below!
Truly yours, - Danny ;)
EDIT: You will get the money once someone is able to login(You may test it, and if you can logon, you will get the money at that moment)
